This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image classification and semantic segmentation. It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it uses low-shot learning techniques. Additionally, it could be categorized under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves training a network to perform a specific task. Neural Networks (cs.NE) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) are also possible sub-categories as the paper involves training a network and making predictions on image data.
